Company Overview of Broadcasting System of Niigata Inc.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Broadcasting System of Niigata Inc. engages in radio and television broadcasting business. It plans, produces, and sells broadcast programs, as well as arts, music, sports, cinema, theater, science, and various entertainments; and plans, issues, and sells publications. The company was founded in 1952 and is headquartered in Niigata, Japan.


